snippet.title: Tales of Graces f Remastered – Announcement Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Tales of Graces f Remastered is coming to Nintendo Switch January 17th, 2025!

Bonds Transcend Time. Tales of Graces f Remastered lets you journey back to the world of Ephinea anywhere you are in the world with the Nintendo Switch.

Journey once again with Asbel and his friends – with visual improvements and downloadable content released in the original!

#TOGfR #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun: https://goo.gl/HYYsot
